    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/2315a2f0869b5a5efe48f3d70eaa0acf.poster.avif?t=1772125543\" width=780 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/2315a2f0869b5a5efe48f3d70eaa0acf.webm?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/2315a2f0869b5a5efe48f3d70eaa0acf.mp4?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无主之地4》中有激烈的战斗、凶狠的秘藏猎人，以及数十亿件狂野致命的武器，全都充斥在一个残酷暴君统治的全新星球中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身四位秘藏猎人之一，横扫凯洛斯星球，追寻财富和荣耀。掌握强大的主动技能，通过深度技能树自定义你的角色，并利用多样的移动能力主宰敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从高高在上、支配众生的残酷独裁者“时间尊者”的压迫中挣脱出来。如今，一场将改变世界的灾难正威胁着他完美的教团，在整个星球上引发了混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/403c8250fdcce402732eddcc9d4b90f4.poster.avif?t=1772125543\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/403c8250fdcce402732eddcc9d4b90f4.webm?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/403c8250fdcce402732eddcc9d4b90f4.mp4?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为势不可挡的战斗力量，利用令人胆寒的全新武器库摧毁敌人。以前所未有的方式穿越无主之地 - 二段跳、滑翔、闪避、抓握等，从各个方位向敌人发动致命打击。释放秘藏猎人的独特能力，利用毁灭性的主动技能引爆每场战斗，利用分支技能树打造你的终极角色，在充满狂暴武器与强力装备的深度战利品追逐中收获满满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/22a4677407eb991547de413fa442d1e2.poster.avif?t=1772125543\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/22a4677407eb991547de413fa442d1e2.webm?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/22a4677407eb991547de413fa442d1e2.mp4?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在凯洛斯肆意破坏，独自爽快，或叫上朋友一起狂嗨！支持4人在线合作！*《无主之地4》自一开始就是专为多人合作打造；无论是搜刮战利品、完成任务，还是自由探索，动态等级调整和个人难度设定都会让队伍始终并肩作战，乐趣不断！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/d7d84b4f3cf4867f6eaa4434197f66a0.poster.avif?t=1772125543\" width=780 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/d7d84b4f3cf4867f6eaa4434197f66a0.webm?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285190/extras/d7d84b4f3cf4867f6eaa4434197f66a0.mp4?t=1772125543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索这片广阔而危险的世界，体验交战派系间的激烈冲突。跨上你的悬浮机车，驰骋在葱郁原野、巍峨山峰与致命荒漠之间，迎战可怕敌人，参与动态事件，踏上充满难忘角色的精彩任务旅程。团结凯洛斯的人民，在这场酣畅淋漓的《无主之地》体验中，利用你认为最恰当的方式，点燃革命之火 <br><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*联机游玩须有互联网连接，跨平台游玩须有SHiFT账户。条款适用。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
